    <briefdescription>
<para>A single set of patient vital sign measurements. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>All fields are captured at the same point in time and treated as a single observation. Callers must ensure values are physically plausible before passing them to validation functions. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
